This rifle in the hands of someone who knows what to do with it is capable of sub-moa shoots out to 1200 yards. If you’re a hunter of four legged prey, make sure you have a good stand to use this one in. The weight soaks up almost all of the recoil, so anyone can use it, even a young teenager just learning about long distance shooting. My price is firm, I really don’t want to sell this one. NO SHIPPING, NO PAYPAL, NO BULLSHIT. If you’ve been saving your tax money for something special, this is it. You pull this rifle out of your case at the range, they know your serious about what your doing.
